divs: Sighting DetailsI was sitting at my computer, which faces our north window, when a bright white colored object flew overhead from south east to north west. I live on the 13th floor of a high rise. Object was fast and silent, sky was overcast. Object was like a fireball except there was no fire...it was just a bright white light moved in a straight line.
